Class Queja

java.lang.Object
edu.uptc.Entidades.PQRS
edu.uptc.Entidades.Queja
public class Queja extends PQRS
Represents a Complaint (Queja) type of PQRS. A complaint expresses dissatisfaction with a service or product. Tracks the level of dissatisfaction and whether it has been reviewed.
